name: Dr. Stanislava Misci
about: Has been teaching and a practicing Prosthodontist in Boston for 18 years. In 2006, she completed her prosthodontics specialty degree at Boston University. She has been a Leading Clear Aligner Specialist since 2010. Dr. Misci completed her Dental Sleep Medicine training in 2020 and became a Diplomate of the American Academy of Dental Sleep Medicine 2021. Dr. Misciâ€™s interest include clear aligners, sleep apnea and airway, facial injectables and esthetic dentistry. Dr. Misci is a Clinical Associate Professor and the immediate past clinical director of the Prosthodontic Patient Treatment Center at Boston University School of Dental Medicine.
